question.string: Does Tokyo have a sea port?
Hat Tokio einen Seehafen?

query.sparql: ASK { ?subject coy:hasLocation ?country . ?subject coy:hasInfrastructureType "port" . ?subject rdfs:label "Tokyo" . ?country rdf:type coy:Country . ?country rdfs:label "Japan"@en. }

question.string: How many sea ports are there in China?
Wie viele Seehafen gibt es in China?

query.sparql: SELECT (COUNT (DISTINCT ?port) AS ?result) WHERE { ?port coy:hasLocation ?country . ?port coy:hasInfrastructureType "port" . ?country rdf:type coy:Country . ?country rdfs:label "People's Republic of China"@en }

question.string: Is there currently a natural disaster in Italy?
Gibt es aktuell eine Naturkatastrophe in Italien?

query.sparql: ASK { ?result rdf:type coy:Disaster . ?result coy:hasCountryLocation ?country . ?result coy:hasStartDate ?sd . ?country rdfs:label "Italy"@en. FILTER(NOT EXISTS {?result coy:hasEndDate ?ed}) }

question.string: When was the last earthquake in Indonesia?
Wann gab es das letzte Erdbeben in Indonesien?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?result WHERE { ?subject rdf:type coy:Disaster . ?subject coy:hasEventType "EQ" . ?subject coy:hasCountryLocation ?country . ?subject coy:hasTimestamp ?result . ?country rdfs:label "Indonesia"@en } ORDER BY DESC(?result) LIMIT 1

question.string: What is the international acronym of Saudi Arabia?
Wie lautet das internationale Kürzel von Saudi-Arabien?

query.sparql: SELECT ?result WHERE { ?subject rdf:type coy:Country . ?subject rdfs:label "Saudi Arabia"@en . ?subject coy:hasIsoCode ?result . }

question.string: What are the last three natural disasters with level orange?
Welches sind die letzten drei Naturkatastrophen mit Level orange?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?result WHERE { ?result rdf:type coy:Disaster . ?result coy:hasAlertScore ?as . ?result coy:hasTimestamp ?ts . FILTER(?as = "2")} ORDER BY DESC(?ts) LIMIT 3

question.string: What is the risk level of Germany?
Wie ist das Risiko-Level von Deutschland?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?result WHERE { ?subject rdf:type coy:Country . ?subject rdfs:label "Germany"@en . ?subject coy:hasRiskLevel ?result . }

question.string: How many disasters happened in 2021 with level 1 or orange?
Wie viele Krisen mit einer Warnmeldung 1 oder orange gab es 2021?

query.sparql: SELECT ( COUNT ( DISTINCT ?dis) AS ?result) WHERE { ?dis rdf:type coy:Disaster . ?dis coy:hasAlertScore ?as . ?dis coy:hasTimestamp ?ts . FILTER ( ( YEAR ( xsd:dateTime ( ?ts ) ) = 2021 ) && ( ?as = "1" ) ) }

question.string: Is there an airport in Kandahar?
Gibt es einen Flughafen in Kandahar?

query.sparql: ASK { ?ap rdf:type coy:Airport . ?ap coy:hasCountry "Afghanistan" . ?ap coy:hasName ?name . FILTER ( regex ( ?name, "Kandahar", "i" ) ) }

question.string: What is the IATA Code of the International Airport in Los Angeles?
Wie ist der IATA Code für den Internationalen Flughafen von Los Angeles?

query.sparql: SELECT ?result WHERE { ?ap rdf:type coy:Airport . ?ap rdfs:label "Los Angeles Intl" . ?ap coy:hasId ?result . }

question.string: How many seaports are located in Europe?
Wie viele Seehäfen gibt es in Europa?

query.sparql: SELECT ( COUNT ( DISTINCT ?seaport ) AS ?result ) WHERE { ?seaport rdf:type coy:Port . ?seaport coy:hasLocation ?country . ?country coy:hasContinentLocation "Europe"@en . }

question.string: What capacity does the biggest powerplant in Japan have?
Welche Kapazität hat das größte Kraftwerk in Japan?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?result WHERE{ ?pp rdf:type coy:Powerplant . ?pp coy:hasCountryLocation/rdfs:label "Japan"@en . ?pp coy:hasCapacity ?result } ORDER BY DESC ( ?result ) LIMIT 1

question.string: What fuel types does the powerplant HKW West use?
Mit welchen Kraftstoffen wird das Kraftwerk HKW West betrieben?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?result WHERE { ?pp rdf:type coy:Powerplant . ?pp coy:hasName "HKW West" . ?pp coy:hasFuelType ?result . }

question.string: How many power plants in India work with gas?
Wie viele Gas-Kraftwerke gibt es in Indien?

query.sparql: SELECT ( COUNT ( DISTINCT ?pp ) AS ?result ) WHERE { ?pp rdf:type coy:Powerplant . ?pp coy:hasFuelType "Gas" . ?pp coy:hasCountryLocation/rdfs:label "India"@en . }

question.string: What was the most recent Disaster that struck in Switzerland?
Was war das letzte katastrophen Ereignis in der Schweiz?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?result WHERE { ?result rdf:type coy:Disaster . ?result coy:hasStartDate ?sd . ?result coy:hasCountryLocation/rdfs:label "Switzerland"@en . } ORDER BY DESC( ?sd ) LIMIT 1

question.string: Was there an active natural disaster in Japan on 2021-01-01?
Gab es am 01.01.2021 in Japan eine Naturkatastrophe?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?dis ?ts ?ts2 WHERE { ?dis rdf:type coy:Disaster . ?dis coy:hasCountryLocation/rdfs:label "Japan"@en . ?dis coy:hasTimestamp ?ts . BIND(xsd:date(?ts) AS ?eventDate)  FILTER(?eventDate = xsd:date("2021-01-01+00:00"))}

question.string: How many companies based in Cologne have more than 10000 employees?
Wie viele Unternehmen in Köln haben mehr als 10.000 Mitarbeiter?

query.sparql: SELECT ( COUNT ( DISTINCT ?comp ) AS ?result ) WHERE { ?comp rdf:type coy:Company . ?comp coy:hasCity "Köln" . ?comp coy:hasNumberOfEmployees ?size . FILTER ( xsd:integer ( ?size ) > 10000 ) }

question.string: Are there more companies in Munich with a size of "small" than "micro"?
Gibt es in München mehr Unternehmen der Größe small als micro?

query.sparql: ASK { { SELECT ( COUNT ( DISTINCT ?comp ) AS ?small) WHERE { ?comp rdf:type coy:Company . ?comp coy:hasCity "München" . ?comp coy:hasCompanySize ?size . FILTER ( ?size = "SMALL" ) } } { SELECT ( COUNT ( DISTINCT ?comp ) AS ?micro ) WHERE { ?comp rdf:type coy:Company . ?comp coy:hasCity "München" . ?comp coy:hasCompanySize ?size . FILTER ( ?size = "MICRO" ) } } FILTER ( ?small > ?micro ) }

question.string: What is the URL of the biggest company (by number of employees) based in Hamburg?
Wie lautet die URL des größten Unternehmens (nach Anzahl an Mitarbeitern) in Hamburg?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?result WHERE { ?comp rdf:type coy:Company . ?comp coy:hasCity "Hamburg" . ?comp coy:hasNumberOfEmployees ?size . ?comp coy:hasUrl ?result } ORDER BY DESC ( xsd:integer ( ?size ) ) LIMIT 1

question.string: Get the EBID-Code of all companies with more than 100,000 employees.
Gib mir den EBID-Code von allen Unternehmen mit mehr als 100.000 Mitarbeitern.

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?result WHERE { ?comp rdf:type coy:Company . ?comp coy:hasEbidCode ?result . ?comp coy:hasNumberOfEmployees ?size .  FILTER ( xsd:integer ( ?size ) > 100000 ) }

question.string: What is the street address of the Deutsche Bahn AG?
Wie lautet die Adresse der Deutsche Bahn AG?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?result WHERE { ?comp rdfs:label "Deutsche Bahn AG" . ?comp coy:hasStreet ?result . }

question.string: Which companies are in the area of the Zip Code 78604?
Welche Unternehmen gibt es im Bereich der Postleitzahl 78604?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?result WHERE { ?result rdf:type coy:Company . ?result coy:hasZip "78604" . }

question.string: How many crises have happenend in Australia since the 2022-01-01?
Wie viele Katastrophen gab es seit dem ersten Januar 2022 in Australien?

query.sparql: SELECT ( COUNT ( DISTINCT ?emergency ) AS ?result ) WHERE { ?emergency rdf:type coy:Disaster . ?emergency coy:hasTimestamp ?ts . ?emergency coy:hasCountryLocation/rdfs:label "Australia"@en . FILTER ( YEAR ( xsd:dateTime ( ?ts ) ) >= 2022 ) }

question.string: Was there an crisis in 2021 that hit both Germany and the Netherlands at the same time?
Gab es 2021 eine Notlage die Deutschland und die Niederlande betraf?

query.sparql: ASK { ?emergency rdf:type coy:Disaster . ?emergency coy:hasStartDate ?ts . ?emergency coy:hasCountryLocation ?loc, ?loc2 . ?loc rdf:type coy:Country . ?loc rdfs:label "Germany"@en . ?loc2 rdf:type coy:Country . ?loc2 rdfs:label "Netherlands"@en . FILTER ( YEAR ( ?ts ) = 2021 ) }

question.string: When was the latest piece of news about russia published on "bloomberg.com"?
Wann gab es die neuesten Nachrichten über Russland auf "bloomberg.com"?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?result WHERE { ?news rdf:type coy:News . ?news coy:hasCountryLocation/rdfs:label "Russia"@en . ?news coy:hasTimestamp ?result . ?news coy:hasUrl ?url . FILTER ( regex ( ?url, "bloomberg.com" ) ) } ORDER BY DESC ( ?result ) LIMIT 1

question.string: How many micro companies are based in Germany?
Wie viele Mikro-Unternehmen gibt es in Deutschland?

query.sparql: SELECT ( COUNT ( DISTINCT ?micro ) AS ?result ) WHERE { ?micro rdf:type coy:Company . ?micro coy:hasCountryLocation/rdfs:label "Germany"@en . ?micro coy:hasCompanySize "MICRO" . }

question.string: Is there at least one Company in the "Gotenstraße"?
Gibt es mindestens ein Unternehmen in der "Gotenstraße"?

query.sparql: ASK { ?comp rdf:type coy:Company . ?comp coy:hasStreet ?street . FILTER ( regex ( ?street, "Gotenstraße" ) ) }

question.string: Which country was plagued by the most disasters in 2021?
Welches Land hatte die meisten Notlagen im Jahr 2021?

query.sparql: SELECT ?result WHERE { ?dis rdf:type coy:Disaster . ?dis coy:hasTimestamp ?ts . ?dis coy:hasCountryLocation/rdfs:label ?result . FILTER ( YEAR ( xsd:dateTime ( ?ts ) ) = 2021 ) } GROUP BY ( ?result ) ORDER BY DESC ( COUNT ( DISTINCT ?dis ) ) LIMIT 1

question.string: What was the latest piece of news relevant to Madagascar about?
Wovon handelte die letzte Madagascar betreffende Nachricht?

query.sparql: SELECT ?result WHERE { ?news rdf:type coy:News . ?news coy:hasCountryLocation/rdfs:label "Madagascar"@en . ?news coy:hasDescription ?result . ?news coy:hasTimestamp ?ts . } ORDER BY DESC ( xsd:dateTime ( ?ts ) ) LIMIT 1

question.string: How many news items have been made about Ukraine in June of 2022?
Wie viele Nachrichten behandelten die Ukraine im Juni 2022?

query.sparql: SELECT ( COUNT ( DISTINCT ?news ) AS ?result ) WHERE { ?news rdf:type coy:News . ?news coy:hasCountryLocation/rdfs:label "Ukraine"@en . ?news coy:hasTimestamp ?ts . FILTER ( ( YEAR ( xsd:dateTime ( ?ts ) ) = 2022 ) && ( MONTH ( xsd:dateTime ( ?ts ) ) = 06 ) ) }

question.string: How many attacks with chemical weapons happened in Brazil in April of 2022?
Wie viele Angrife mit chemischen Waffen passierten im April 2022 in Brazilien?

query.sparql: SELECT ( COUNT ( DISTINCT ?event ) AS ?result ) WHERE { ?event rdf:type coy:ChemicalWeapon . ?event coy:hasIsoCode ?iso . ?event coy:hasTimestamp ?ts . ?country rdf:type coy:Country . ?country rdfs:label "Brazil"@en . ?country coy:hasIso3Code ?iso . FILTER ( (YEAR ( ?ts ) = 2022 ) && ( MONTH ( ?ts ) = 04 ) ) }

question.string: How many attacks happened in Kherson in 2022?
Wie viele Attacken gab es 2022 in Cherson?

query.sparql: SELECT ( COUNT ( DISTINCT ?attack ) AS ?result ) WHERE { ?attack rdf:type coy:Attack . ?attack coy:hasLocation "Kherson" . ?attack coy:hasTimestamp ?ts . FILTER ( YEAR ( ?ts ) = 2022 ) }

question.string: Was Odesa attacked in 2020?
Wurde Odessa in 2020 angegriffen?

question.string: What are the indices of the 3 northernmost harbors in Europe?
Wie lauten die Indizes der drei nördlichsten Häfen in Europa?

question.string: How many interventions against Russia are currently active?
